data.description: This is your opportunity to put in some sweat equity or make this place your own. New Carpet/flooring/paint would do wonders!    Enjoy breathtaking mountain views right from your living room and bedroom windows. This 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo offers 1,137 square feet of comfortable living space.    The open floor plan is flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living area features forced air heating and central air conditioning, ensuring year-round comfort. Stay cozy with your gas fireplace while you enjoy a glass of wine or morning coffee.    The kitchen provides ample counter space and over looks the living room. Step out onto the private balcony to savor your morning coffee or evening sunset while gazing at the picturesque mountain vistas.    Enjoy the on site gym, pool, and hot tub included in your HOA dues while soaking up the mountain views.    Both bedrooms are spacious, and the master suite boasts an ensuite bathroom for added convenience. This property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility, with shopping, dining, and outdoor adventures just moments away.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this condo your new mountain-view retreat in Colorado Springs!
